# S-Clip ğŸ¥  

**S-Clip** is a lightweight, high-performance screen clipping and recording software for Windows.  
It allows users to **instantly clip the last 30 seconds** of their screen or manually **record and stop** with ease.  

---

## ğŸš€ Features
âœ… **Instant Replay Clipping** - Press a hotkey to save the last 30 seconds of your screen.  
âœ… **Manual Recording Mode** - Start and stop recording whenever you want.  
âœ… **Customizable Settings** - Adjust resolution, FPS, encoder, and more.  
âœ… **Minimal Performance Impact** - Optimized FFmpeg usage for low CPU/GPU overhead.  
âœ… **Modern UI** - Clean and stylish dark theme with purple accents.  
âœ… **Fully Open Source** - Modify and improve as needed!

